What's Changed
Important
This release includes a significant rewrite of the store's scoping internals for better performance and memory management. Please test your application thoroughly when upgrading to this release.
Added: Store now conforms to the
ObservableObject
(
#3625
). This conformance does not provide any observation via
@ObservedObject
, and is provided as a convenience to allow stores to be held in
@StateObject
s. Store observation should continue to be done via the Observation framework (or Perception package) and the
@ObservableState
macro.
Fixed: Store internals have been rewritten for performance and better memory management (
#3460
